30
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,769
How much?

31
00:02:40,489 --> 00:02:42,238
No idea...

32
00:02:42,348 --> 00:02:45,849
I may just accept it right away!

33
00:02:46,009 --> 00:02:48,949
